snippet.title: Little Oliver's Magical Carousel Adventure - Journey Through Various Professions
snippet.description:
Little Oliver rides on a carousel and transforms into a worker to try different professions. What professions does he try? Little Oliver's magical carousel adventure!

00:00 Oliver plays Professions
04:49 Oliver pretends to be a vet
09:17 Roma Opens His Own Kindergarten
